From ac2037db146be1d8cba5b38e77aba8f9ae426e27 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: DAF <danielarifriedman@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 17:01:35 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] feat: comprehensive expansion to full Triple-Stream Active
 Inference lab
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Content (10 modules × 3 streams = 30 experiences)
- Modules 2-10 completed across Pulse, Vision, and Core streams covering
  the Parr/Pezzulo/Friston (2022) textbook: generative models, POMDPs,
  belief propagation, EFE decomposition, continuous flow (generalized
  coordinates, action law), model-based data analysis (RFX-BMS, PEB),
  and the whole orbit.
- Shared StreamTemplate + useStreamProgress pattern across all modules.

New interactive components
- BeliefChart, ConceptMap, DataFitter, FreeEnergyField, GenerativeGraph,
  GridWorld, MessagePassingCircuit, ModelRecipe, Quiz.

New surfaces
- /glossary (search + letter-jump + module cross-links)
- /search (fuzzy scoring across modules + glossary)
- /settings (reduced-motion, high-contrast, font-scale, haptics, sound,
  default stream, math default, auto-bookmark, reset controls)
- /404 NotFoundPage
- TopBar quick-nav; BottomNav kept for primary journeys.

Enhanced existing pages
- HomePage: Up-next card, overall progress, quick-link tiles.
- ModuleListPage: tag filters, per-stream pips, outcomes preview, minutes
  badges, completion states.
- ModulePage: outcomes + glossary chips overview, per-stream progress.
- HearthPage: 15 badges, 28-day sparkline, per-module journey bars,
  session timeline, good-questions list.

System
- SettingsContext drives runtime a11y via CSS custom-properties and
  data-attributes (reduced-motion, high-contrast, font-scale).
- Design tokens: semantic aliases + high-contrast + reduced-motion
  branches; font-scale via calc on html root.
- resetApp() clears progress/activity/settings localStorage.
- PWA: manifest.webmanifest + versioned service worker (cache-first
  static, network-first nav, /index.html offline fallback), registered
  in production only.
- Code splitting: React.lazy at the route level AND per-module; initial
  JS bundle 771 kB → 385 kB (gzip 237 kB → 124 kB); KaTeX isolated to a
  lazy 258 kB chunk; each module ships as a 3-14 kB on-demand chunk.
- Build: 531 modules transformed, 363 ms, zero warnings.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
